# Each component has its own .env.example — use the one for what you're running:
#
#   n8n workflow      →  n8n/.env.example
#   FastAPI + CLI     →  backend/.env.example  (copy to repo root as .env)
#
# Quick start for the CLI runner:
#   cp backend/.env.example .env
#   # Fill in at minimum: GROQ_API_KEY or ANTHROPIC_API_KEY
#   python backend/scripts/run_pipeline.py
